					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Woooow XD this reminds me of an old idea that I had in my mind about a Smash-like NES game, but I couldn't make it because it was too low level for me. I was concerned about the pallettes issue since every character would take one sprite pallette which would ultimately take all 4 spaces. And I was also concerned about the 8 sprites per scanline issue. Like, what if you have 4 players next to each other and one of them fires a projectile? You'll surely get flickering! So how do you manage to fix that?</div>

